# type(scope): short summary
#
# Types:
# feat     - New feature
# fix      - Bug fix
# docs     - Documentation
# style    - Code style changes
# refactor - Code refactoring
# test     - Adding tests
# chore    - Maintenance

# Example:
# feat(user): add create user endpoint


